---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/ui/Footer.astro'
import { footerConfig } from '../data/footer'
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/easyyield-logo.png" />
  <link rel="preload" href="/tailwind.css?v=20260625c" as="style">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/tailwind.css?v=20260625c">
  <style>html,body{font-family:Inter,system-ui,-apple-system}</style>
  <script>window.FontAwesomeConfig = { autoReplaceSvg: 'nest'};</script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/js/all.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></script>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" />
  <title>Privacy Policy - Easy Yield</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Easy Yield Privacy Policy — how we collect, use, and protect your personal information." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://easyyield.ca/privacy" />
</head>
<body>
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <p class="text-sm text-amber-600 font-medium mb-2">Legal</p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">Last updated: June 2026</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-8">

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">1. Who We Are</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Easy Yield ("we," "us," or "our") operates <strong>easyyield.ca</strong>, a Canadian personal-finance comics and vlog site. We are committed to protecting your personal information and being transparent about how we use it.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">
              For privacy-related inquiries, contact us at: <a href="mailto:info@easyyield.ca" class="text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700">info@easyyield.ca</a>
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">We collect information you provide directly to us, including:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
              <li><strong>Account information:</strong> name, email address, and password when you create an account</li>
              <li><strong>Newsletter subscriptions:</strong> email address and optional first/last name when you subscribe to our mailing list</li>
              <li><strong>Communications:</strong> messages you send us via email or contact forms</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">We also automatically collect limited technical information such as your IP address, browser type, and pages visited when you use our website, solely for security and performance purposes.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
              <li>To send our newsletter and author updates <em>only if you have subscribed and verified your email address</em></li>
              <li>To respond to contact form messages and reader inquiries</li>
              <li>To improve our website</li>
              <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for their marketing purposes.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">4. Email Communications & Subscriptions</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              When you subscribe to our newsletter, we require email verification before sending any marketing emails. Unverified addresses are automatically removed from our system within a few days.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              You may unsubscribe at any time by clicking the "Unsubscribe" link at the bottom of any email we send, or by contacting us directly. We will remove you promptly — no questions asked.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              For full details on how we manage subscriber data, please see our <a href="/data-use-policy" class="text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700">Data Use Policy</a>.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">5. Data Retention</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              We retain your account data for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide services and comply with legal obligations. Newsletter subscriber data is retained only while you are an active, verified subscriber. Unverified subscription requests are automatically deleted within days of the initial request.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">
              You may delete your account and all associated data at any time directly from the <strong>Account</strong> menu — no need to contact support.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">6. Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              We use essential cookies to keep you logged in and maintain your session. We do not use advertising or tracking cookies. No third-party analytics cookies are placed on your device.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">7. Security</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              We use industry-standard encryption (TLS/HTTPS) for all data in transit. Passwords are stored as one-way hashes and are never readable by our team.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">8. Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">You have the right to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
              <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
              <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
              <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
              <li>Withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">
              To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:info@easyyield.ca" class="text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-700">info@easyyield.ca</a>.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Material changes will be announced on our website. Continued use of our services after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
            </p>
          </section>

        </div>

        <!-- Related policies -->
        <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/data-use-policy" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-200 rounded-lg text-sm text-neutral-700 transition-colors">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-file-lines text-amber-500"></i>Data Use Policy
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-200 rounded-lg text-sm text-neutral-700 transition-colors">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope text-amber-500"></i>Contact
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer {...footerConfig} />
</body>
</html>
